  <brief_title>Studying Non-motor Symptoms in SPG4</brief_title>
  <official_title>Studying Non-motor Symptoms in Patients With Hereditary Spastic Paraplegia (HSP) Type 4 (SPG4) Compared to Healthy Controls</official_title>
