  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparing the non-motor symptoms of patients with SPG4 mutations to healthy controls
      (spouses, relatives or other healthy controls) by using the a number of specific
      questionaires
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      https://lamapoll.de/NMS_in_HSP
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
